Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  汤乃鹭温泉街人才可真是多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么重磅的器材都拿来了啊  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为摄影师搞过特摄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  应该说那才是他的本行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  那么换下一个场景吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘  现在您方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.99,0:03:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回了一趟久违的家乡  让你患上思乡病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  我就开门见山地说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有人上门谈拍电影的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有接受那件事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我交给缘处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那件事很蹊跷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈你只要出面说一句不就结了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次这件事我完全没有插手的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿不愿意继承这家旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  继承喜翠庄的人是缘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是  那个人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承喜翠庄的是缘啊  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我说了些多余的话了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是多余的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也已经结了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该是少爷来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…那一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了  真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.05,0:04:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍电影了？  没想到会做这些事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是会用十二万分的细致来服务客人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我们已经深蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才从窗子跳下去的你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心跳都差点停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是这样的话  接下来一些场景还是请您回避的好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.17,0:05:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的电影是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划书上写的是青春女服务员吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的电影呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同业公会的老板娘们好像都不太喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  在尝试些新事物的时候人们都会不安的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是别人在做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是别人挑战新事物  还成功了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说谁不会眼红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会有让那么多家的老板娘同时出现的镜头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.41,0:06:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  老板娘们趁着公休旅行来温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后所有人都变成僵尸之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦送两份去桐之间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿去藤之间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贴着红签的那个是没放葱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  难怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事情难怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才藤之间的客人盯着我的脸看个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去藤之间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就是正式的拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请您多多关照  伊佐美先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请各位好好期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放水了  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说是一出骗局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当初就觉得事有蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗局？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边凉快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄也大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没和伊佐美先生联系上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  发了我一封邮件说企划终止后就没消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再跟你联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚开始就觉得有些蹊跷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐你可没这么说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我没跟你提过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急着汇款  确认安全无误之后再来操作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.51,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确是有这么说过…  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  合同上签的名字是缘先生你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事是崇子小姐你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白…我当然明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷他怎么样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.11,0:09:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像拿出了不少资金
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然轻信那女人的花言巧语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱说话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了「伊佐美辙夫」这名字听起来不觉得很像「得意忘形重蹈覆辙」么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去削萝卜皮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道彻先生很不考虑场合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我觉得就算这样也不影响做一名好厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.88,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  电影这件事情好像泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想上荧幕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也很想上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.64,0:10:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家明明都很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得能过上一个印象深刻的暑假来的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜她也非常期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心喜翠庄是不是会有大麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就一路跑过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看来没这回事  放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你不是刚来么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不是很清楚内幕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我自言自语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊佐美辙夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人以前有过两次逃债的前科
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎早就被排挤出了影视圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱多半都被花到还债上去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要收回那笔钱大概会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:15.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被扯进这件事的演员和工作人员们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来这一阵时间也很难做人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然给你打个电话真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也不想再说什么丧气话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今我仍觉得我的初衷是没有错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.06,0:11:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过作为经营者结果才是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我想你应该很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对职员们应负的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有对客人们应负的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子那么严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能所有人想做就能成功…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是草莓味棒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想打扫一下泳池周围
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是电影已经没戏了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近几天一直都在打扫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像养成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做就感觉不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.94,0:12:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小姑娘们也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民子也刚去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们两个一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是为了电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.05,0:13:03.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我先去一趟东京
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多必须要做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个我清楚…我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没时间再陪少爷瞎折腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎折腾…我们不是搭档吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭档…这次企划的最高负责人是少爷你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是顾问而已  顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是崇子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合同不也是两个人一起递出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不都是一起思考  一起讨论的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话  废话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这些废话去找你那引以为豪的姐姐说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.64,0:14:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二话不说就使用暴力这点真是和老板娘一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  一不当心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经反射
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐你是能够反击的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里纠结责任什么的也于事无补
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看崇子小姐帅气的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看平时的崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We strike back I shall
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…We shall return！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在乱说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是所有事用用英文就能解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是正确
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.14,0:14:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.39,0:15:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  请再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…命…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是想让我抓住还是放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经尽全力了  但这就是我的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,max limit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍受不住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吗  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是职业的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会就这样结束的  在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够得着池底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么赔我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我的胜负装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负装？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  你可要赔我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成这样了  很贵的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把胜负装穿来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.73,0:16:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  所以我都说了很贵的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐是认真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.35,0:16:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种头脑简单的思考方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就是你这个人的缺点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.92,0:16:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们两个再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.27,0:16:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要两人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就都只想着自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再看下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.06,0:17:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也想要做下父母该做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄今后也要辛苦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不太想说…不过也是自作自受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让他之前那么得意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很舒服呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从二楼的窗户跳下来有点飞舞的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这样的镜头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真是不幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这次事件的始末
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先我想亲口报告给各位汤乃鹭的代表们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.01,0:18:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才来访于此的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波之间的  做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤之间  生鱼片两人份还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.44,0:18:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤之间的我拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.26,0:18:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来我房间一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都做得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来应该由我去说明的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是川尻小姐真的是为喜翠庄考虑才…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事也是全心全意投入了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都必须要让川尻小姐来负这个责的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.45,0:19:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在称呼老妈也行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.75,0:19:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老妈  我并不是在包庇她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真的是真心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事等会再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然变得会如此的袒护别人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:20:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还很顽固  还是该说不明事理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净是做些让人费解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指去上钢琴课的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想过  如果学会一件乐器的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能受女生欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已经那样劝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却打死也不肯去学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候如果硬让我去学的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.76,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我的青春就完全不一样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连游泳也完全不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳就算现在也是三脚猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了  原稿完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的云彩
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是人鱼公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.95,0:23:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会憧憬王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.45,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为陆地好可怕呀
